layerGroup.title: National Outfall Database (Clean Ocean Foundation)
layerGroup.abstractTxt:
The National Outfall Database (NOD) maps the marine impacts of wastewater disposal to ocean and estuarine waters in Australia. The database currently tracks 29 indicators across 178 monitoring sites.
This data was last updated 30/06/21 from https://www.outfalls.info/
